<li>I am so deeply sorry to hear about the loss of your sister.</li>
<li>My heart goes out to you during this incredibly difficult time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending you all my love and support.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, whatever you need, anytime.</li>
<li>Your sister was a truly special person; I'll cherish the memories I have of her.</li>
<li>Please don't hesitate to reach out if you need someone to talk to.</li>
